# Defence-in-depth — `test/grep-gate.test.ts` writes intentional
# violation fixtures into this directory to verify the gate catches
# them. Cleanup happens in a `beforeAll`/`afterAll` PLUS a per-test
# `finally`, but if all three fail this gitignore is the last line
# of defence preventing a leftover fixture from being committed.
src/_grep_gate_test_violation/
